(44, 17, 20, 40, 19, 23, 25, 'we would know therefore what these things mean', 'Wealth and Understanding Salvation', 'This connection highlights the theme of understanding the challenges of salvation, particularly for those with wealth. Both passages emphasize the difficulty of entering the kingdom of God, prompting a desire for clarity about salvation.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
